<p>The post <a href="https://newsnetwork.mayoclinic.org/discussion/mayo-clinic-researcher-harnesses-uniqueness-of-space-to-advance-medicine-on-earth/">Mayo Clinic researcher harnesses uniqueness of space to advance medicine on Earth</a> appeared first on <a href="https://newsnetwork.mayoclinic.org">Mayo Clinic News Network</a>.</p>
